Gunman Kills Four, Injures 16 in Attack on Shopping Center Near Amsterdam

-- B y   M a a i k e   N o o r d h u i s
-- 
2011-04-09T12:40:13Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-09/four-people-killed-16-others-injured-in-dutch-mall-shooting.html
At least four people have been
killed after a man armed with a machine gun opened fire at a
Dutch shopping mall.  Sixteen other people have been injured in the incident in
Alphen aan den Rijn, a city 13 miles south-west of Amsterdam,
the city said in a statement today.  The gunman killed himself, eyewitnesses told Dutch
broadcaster NOS. The city mall has been cleared and a wide area
around it is cordoned off.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Maaike Noordhuis in Amsterdam 
 mnoordhuis@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
